summary: I joined the University of Twente in October 2015. I graduated with BSc and MSc in Mathematics at Addis Ababa University, Ethiopia. I did my PhD in Applied Statistics (Measurement and Evaluation) at the University of Groningen. I served both in academic and administrative affairs at various universities.
